{"kind":"symbol","sections":[],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Sets whether to show alert for push notifications when app is in foreground."}],"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"platforms":["iOS"],"languages":["occ"],"tokens":[{"text":"+ (","kind":"text"},{"text":"void","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:v"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"text":"setShowPushnotificationAlert:","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"text":"BOOL","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:@T@BOOL"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"kind":"internalParam","text":"show"},{"text":";","kind":"text"}]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"kind":"parameters","parameters":[{"name":"show","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"YES to show alerts in foreground, NO to suppress them (default)"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"anchor":"discussion","level":2,"text":"Discussion","type":"heading"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"By default, iOS does not display notification banners when the app is in the foreground."},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"Enable this to show system notification alerts even when the app is active."}]},{"level":2,"anchor":"Example","text":"Example","type":"heading"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Configure based on app type:","type":"text"}]},{"code":["class NotificationConfigManager {","","    func configureForAppType(_ appType: AppType) {","        switch appType {","        case .messaging:","            \/\/ Messaging apps typically handle notifications in-app","            Pushwoosh.configure.setShowPushnotificationAlert(false)","","        case .ecommerce, .news:","            \/\/ E-commerce and news apps benefit from showing all notifications","            Pushwoosh.configure.setShowPushnotificationAlert(true)","","        case .game:","            \/\/ Games might want to suppress during gameplay","            Pushwoosh.configure.setShowPushnotificationAlert(false)","        }","    }","","    func temporarilyDisableForegroundAlerts(during action: () -> Void) {","        let wasEnabled = Pushwoosh.configure.getShowPushnotificationAlert()","        Pushwoosh.configure.setShowPushnotificationAlert(false)","","        action()","","        Pushwoosh.configure.setShowPushnotificationAlert(wasEnabled)","    }","}"],"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"code":"UNUserNotificationCenterDelegate","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" and use ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"Pushwoosh.ForegroundPush"},{"type":"text","text":"."}]}]}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore","doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration"]]},"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration\/setShowPushnotificationAlert:","interfaceLanguage":"occ"},"metadata":{"symbolKind":"method","title":"setShowPushnotificationAlert:","externalID":"c:objc(pl)PWConfiguration(cm)setShowPushnotificationAlert:","modules":[{"name":"PushwooshCore"}],"role":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"+ ","kind":"text"},{"text":"setShowPushnotificationAlert:","kind":"identifier"}],"roleHeading":"Type Method","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"setShowPushnotificationAlert:","kind":"identifier"}]},"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"patch":0,"major":0},"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration\/setshowpushnotificationalert:"]}],"references":{"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore/PWConfiguration":{"kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration","type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration","abstract":[],"role":"symbol","title":"PWConfiguration","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"PWConfiguration"}]},"doc://com.pushwoosh.P